{"tid":326453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"轟警「砌生豬肉冇成本」","createTime":"2017-07-18T04:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T09:54:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05dedb86a3ff6316db1f2c8cfc789c5d57d45346","tid":326453,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20093237&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20093237%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170718&d=%2F8JwxMpE5qC8u%2FkABUisASwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b8a62e06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20093237%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170718&h=78c638f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20093237&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170718</a><br />\n<br />\n轟警「砌生豬肉冇成本」<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170718/large/18la5p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170718%2Flarge%2F18la5p6.jpg&h=c110ac42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告孫君和被捕時遭警打至頭破血流，昨被裁定罪名不成立。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨被裁定罪名不成立的陳紹鈞在散庭後稱，裁決未還他公道，他批評警長誣告他掟磚，沒良知，擔心執法者「砌生豬肉」會變成常態，「砌生豬肉冇成本，砌唔入都冇代價，驚佢哋會做更多呢啲事。」他考慮或向警方索償。<br />\n陳散庭後不忿說：「想問吓誣告我掟磚嘅警長，點去面對佢嘅家人、子女同太太？用咁卑劣嘅行為誣告普通巿民，對我嘅家庭、小朋友有好大影響！」<br />\n<br />\n考慮向警索償<br />\n<br />\n陳說做每一件事都光明正大，今次雖被控，但無阻他繼續做公民記者，只是經一事長一智，以後拍攝時不會跑，亦不會提早關掉攝錄機。他稱早有心理準備會被入罪，亦同時擔心一旦罪成會令家庭支離破碎。他育有兩名分別4歲及14歲的兒子，但他沒跟長子交代太多與案有關的事情。他又表示會考慮向警方索償。<br />\n另一無罪獲釋的被告孫君和對裁決不願多談，只說以平常心面對結果。<br />\n■記者黃幗慧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t旺角騷亂　首有人脫暴動罪　官指警作供有疑點　兩被告當庭釋放<br />\n要聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"ca60e3cd8234c3fd7f223f4f370e71fbaf70cdd6","tid":326453,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b123c4c53c179965ae0cc7ac44aafe4385d5b22f","tid":326453,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:30:19.000Z","msg":"點解會冇成本？"},{"pid":"6349194027ceb7258ccb3e88b977c136e207f382","tid":326453,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"而家比假口供唔係刑事？"},{"pid":"7aebf558a19262c9050bb997855f52830d91f288","tid":326453,"uid":55077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會冇成本？</blockquote><br />\n個成本係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7255cd634b9158afe2ebbc6fc8a5c6ec88ef6ae6","tid":326453,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"警犬老屈人已經同港女老屈非禮接近一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ac11d8c274c71a038e1361ad35ebc5cff471c5","tid":326453,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解會冇成本？</blockquote><br />\n個成本係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n響法庭講大話唔係刑事？"},{"pid":"be567bfcc154f65e431236612cf2f2760bb64d14","tid":326453,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:33:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解會冇成本？</blockquote><br />\n個成本係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgm